scratchpad.client.todolist
Class ToDoListManager

java.lang.Object
  scratchpad.client.todolist.ToDoListManager

public class ToDoListManager
extends java.lang.Object

This is a ToDoList Manager Object which is responsible everything about to - do List structure. To-to list manager responsible for creating, editing, deleting ,opening ,holding todo list dialogs and every to-do list dialog is responsible for holding the to-doList object it represents and ,create,edit,delete tasks on this object.

Author:
Huseyin
